2 0 2 2 😍 

Unbelievable amount of good came from 2022. So grateful for this life and family I’ve been blessed with! Here’s to 2023! 🍻

One of these years I’m going to #sheepshow , until then, I’ll keep reliving my own sheep week! This hunt was 3 years ago, almost to the day…. Time flies!
•
•
•
#bowhunting #desertsheep #desertbighorn #ramdown #foxjenkins2020hunts

For my dads birthday, I wanted to do something special. He’s always loved displaying some of the bigger sheds I’ve picked up. So I decided to throw a couple brown sets on a @borderlandsupply XL Pack! Turned out really cool and he absolutely loved it!! 

You make a rad product, Colter!👊

#borderlandsupply #oldschooltrapperpack #shedhunting #elksheds #browngold #shedseason #elkhorn #elk #elkhunting #homedecor #barnwooddecor

Before >>>> After! 

Had such a riot with these mighty hog hunters! 🐖🐖

I was somewhat curious how this type of hunt would go, but it’s definitely something I’d do I again. 

You know what they say- Good company makes for an even better time! 

#pighunting #boarhunting #razorbackhogs #europeanboars @kingscamo

Gotta give my wife @melfoxy MAJOR props for keeping her cool, like always, during the chaos of this pig hunt. She made a standing shot at 230 yards and the pig didn’t go 20 yards. Nice work babe!!! 😘 

Thanks @kkdoxey for borrowing us the rifle, thing can shoot and makes me want a suppressor real bad! 

#pighunting #girlshunttoo #oneshotonekill

Summertime…. Counting down the hours at this point! I’m excited to scout new/old areas and hopefully find a few bucks worth chasing! 

#bowhunting #archeryhunting #archerymuledeer #archeryelk #velvetbucks #summerscouting #highcountrymuledeer #hunting #elkhunting

Opening Weekend! 🏹🦌

We had a great time in Mule Deer country. We tried our best to make my nephew a bowhunter for life and although he didn’t tag out, I think we were successful! He had multiple stalks and got within bow range twice! The adrenaline from bow hunting is unmatched. Such good times!!!

#foxjenkins2023hunts #bowhunting #archery #muledeer #velvetbucks #kingscamo #sliktripods #evolutionoutdoors #psebows #aaearchery #blackgoldsights #tightspotquivers #apexnextevolution

I’ve been anticipating this moment since the day this kid was born!!!

Not only did Maxxon tag out on his very first buck, he did it on his 12th birthday! 1 shot at 490 yards is all it took. Swipe to see the shot! 

Hunting together has brought me so much joy. I hope he grows into a passionate hunter. Seeing his emotions before, during, and after the shot tells me he will be! 

I’m so proud of you buddy!

Let’s get more birthday bucks in the future!
